<item>
            <title>[LU-3887] lfs lsetfacl and lfs rsetfacl fail to generate changelog records</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3887</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;lfs ACL control commands lsetfacl and rsetfacl fail to generate changelog records.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Standard setfacl commands do generate XATTR changelog events.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;-cf&lt;/p&gt;</description>
